WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.838
(KNOCKING)

00:00:01.376 --> 00:00:03.344
(WHISPERING) Jamie. Hey.
(WHISPERING) Hey.

00:00:03.670 --> 00:00:04.842
You up? Yeah. Come in.

00:00:07.799 --> 00:00:09.597
I thought you were going to bed.
I was.

00:00:09.676 --> 00:00:12.350
But then I realized we were
both single again, so...

00:00:12.971 --> 00:00:14.018
Oopsy. (GASPS)

00:00:14.347 --> 00:00:15.394
Oopsy.

00:00:16.057 --> 00:00:17.684
Dude, no. Why not?

00:00:17.809 --> 00:00:19.686
I washed my hands.
With soap this time.

00:00:19.853 --> 00:00:21.730
Are you serious?
Why would you just assume?

00:00:21.896 --> 00:00:25.571
You cracked your neck on the porch.
This thing. That's your tell, remember?

00:00:25.734 --> 00:00:29.034
I cracked my neck because we
were on a flight for six hours,

00:00:29.696 --> 00:00:32.575
and you were yapping my ear off about
how planes all fly themselves,

00:00:32.699 --> 00:00:34.201
and it actually kinked
my neck a bit.

00:00:34.326 --> 00:00:37.045
So, no?
No. Not having sex with you.

00:00:37.162 --> 00:00:39.415
