They have an app for that. No, wait.

00:00:42.375 --> 00:00:44.343
Nope, you're good to go.
We talked about this.

00:00:44.419 --> 00:00:47.093
Plus, I just got dumped, so...
Okay, I'm sorry.

00:00:47.213 --> 00:00:49.511
I thought this would be a good
way to take your mind off him.

00:00:49.591 --> 00:00:51.719
No, I don't function that way.
Sex is not gonna help.

00:00:52.177 --> 00:00:54.305
But you know what will?
Emotional support.

00:00:54.387 --> 00:00:57.266
Before we were sex without emotion,
and now we're emotion without sex.

00:00:57.390 --> 00:00:58.812
Exactly.

00:00:58.892 --> 00:01:00.735
I just need you
to be my friend right now.

00:01:00.852 --> 00:01:02.900
Okay. So I'll listen to you
while you give me a hand job.

00:01:03.188 --> 00:01:05.532
No. I'm kidding.
I got it. Good night.

00:01:05.774 --> 00:01:09.779
Wait, hold on! Friends can still hang
out and, I don't know, listen to music.

00:01:10.028 --> 00:01:11.029
Listen to music?

